x;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">各种史诗级大片纷纷出炉，逼真的效果、震撼的场面让网友们震惊到失语。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">比如B站UP主「AI疯人院」的这部2024开篇王炸——AI版西游记动画短片，已经取得了将近百万的播放量。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="87" data-backw="578" data-imgfileid="504965726" data-ratio="0.15053763440860216" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="930" style="width: 78%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPicdJVSYRwXFj5aQSkogtMuohUunohjKLRugWmFlyFSWJlHhdHCzpicRA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="277" data-backw="578" data-imgfileid="504965730" data-ratio="0.4796875" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="640" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPIibBH6dTdlhxpFjuricqdBOOlwEmnDGdic2jOLbbmys5flCSKejT7tLpg/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">网友们纷纷惊呼，开篇就被惊艳到，整个看下来感受就是：简直绝了！</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="212" data-backw="562" data-height="327" data-imgfileid="504965729" data-ratio="0.37066974595842955" data-type="png" data-w="866" data-width="866" height="321" style="width: 78%;height: auto !important;" width="866" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPAOHr76mutSLIUjSjcZJBSia1Mz3iaFkt57meJicIQ0Dp0tcPhcQGQNcuw/640?wx_fmt=png"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="141" data-backw="562" data-height="297" data-imgfileid="504965728" data-ratio="0.25" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1187" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPibVJJKtAC7taaPPNvotPGpOoOtpnnINKAdh0ZXjDaHOUwK9m2wCJupw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">而一位名叫Shang Chi的小哥做出的AI电影「怀旧宇航员」，则让无数人落泪，直接入选今年MIT AI电影大赛的最佳影片。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="263" data-backw="480" data-imgfileid="504965734" data-ratio="0.5479166666666667" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="480" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJP3ADR8ibic4AO075hT9pWlNRfErj2FuUP01K1IFvNU2dRVGI5wctUibYfA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;"></span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">所以，我们离自己DIY出一部AI大片，到底有多远？</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">虽然，最近爆红的Sora把视频时间延长到了史诗级的60秒，但离一整部电影大片的时长，还是差得远。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">不过，刚刚出炉的一套AI工具，直接把电影制作的整个工作流都给实现了！</span></p><div autoid="1895" data-style-type="0" style="max-width: 100%;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div style="padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"></span>AI大电影「完整工作流」来了</p></div></div><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;">就在刚刚，以色列</span>初创公司Lightricks正式发布了<span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;">一款</span><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;">AI驱动的电影生成和剪辑软件——</span>LTX Studio。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">只要通过文字，它就能直接生成复杂的剧情，包含语音、音效、视频画面，一整套全包圆了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="367" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504965731" data-ratio="0.6532846715328468" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="822" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPcLrq5ebTy7NliaWTWonibnbQQibfk2dKM4wH9xWIcOrIgSaFibea9xO8ww/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;">联合创始人（从左至右）：Itai Tsiddon、Yaron Inger、Zeev Farbman、Amit Goldstein和Nir Pochter</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">它包含的一整套导演工具，直接重新定义了视频制作的工作流！其中包括自动编写脚本工具、调整多镜头的场景控制工具、保证角色一致性的工具、摄像机控制、一键编辑等等。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这样，我们制作出高质量视频，就更轻松了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">只要你给出一个初步想法，LTX Studio就能把你的想法可视化。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">比如，现在我们的电影中需要一只因惊讶而放大的瞳孔。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="311" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504965732" data-ratio="0.553125" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="640" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPXpicu2cgVG487TW7icgr7HYxbZdgS5j8ibau9PwB9Hp8ziajOk1VGCNJtQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">一个躺在地上的女人。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="285" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504965733" data-ratio="0.5074074074074074" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPorWPdLnklzKDqeCkaIjh78CnoDsvj0NHmOkRHmpXE5NfCMct77CGXA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">一个被水淹了的未来主义房间中的一棵树。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="285" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504965735" data-ratio="0.5074074074074074" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPKfunRra2bXhQxMw2abDcDd38TNeb031K5Nia0xdLLVYbKX2jEZRXhwA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">昏暗走廊中的一个女人。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="285" data-backw="562" data-height="1104" data-imgfileid="504965736" data-ratio="0.5074074074074074" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="2174" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPGIWelmpg0bfpGdG8dvkbF8YggGAbiax30ZkBpNlkPicBxOaJmZAAo3gQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">一个恶棍。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="285" data-backw="562" data-height="1104" data-imgfileid="504965737" data-ratio="0.5074074074074074" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="2174" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPibPWdZ0RRrlD0Va2zMUuOyhMBp7X1VvricO7pFv7WWuEdniaP6rJ28aPA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">根据你输入的prompt，LTX Studio自动为创建出了脚本，分割出众多个镜头。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">比如一个未来主义空间的戏剧场景，它创建出的镜头如下。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="311" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504965739" data-ratio="0.553125" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="640" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPURYvPib90k7MDNwia9s8mb8tvswaNBDEGibgSN649V5Q8kFg6QIkuGBug/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">或者，我们需要纽约法庭的场景。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="311" data-backw="562" data-height="355" data-imgfileid="504965738" data-ratio="0.553125" data-type="gif" data-w="640" data-width="641" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPcQsJZjZUC9qE6h1o0oME7b4u8hcsPKTETPLbZWkdJxaMLg9w0nONQQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">有了这些分镜头之后，就可以直接让它生成一部电影了！</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="307" data-backw="562" data-height="350" data-imgfileid="504965740" data-ratio="0.546875" data-type="gif" data-w="640" data-width="640" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPuksJvvNXYhibsRNFuj7C2RAz5f6s3ggFDB2bZyCClLzzAibhKWCzpkgQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">自动生成的故事板，会组织起整个的叙事和场景规划，对角色、摄像机角度都能自定义控制。这种直观的体验，让前期制作和粗剪都更迅速。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">而它生成的画面内容，比如演员、造型、场景，都可以随意剪辑更换。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">比如，刚才生成影片中男人背后的绿车，我们想让它变成红色的，一秒给你改变。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="307" data-backw="562" data-height="350" data-imgfileid="504965743" data-ratio="0.546875" data-type="gif" data-w="640" data-width="640" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPum6ibWmIN69VdkhGfEBlqhwdGrpSMf92c9rQksmar0ox6M1EzeE328Q/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">可以让肌肉女变成肌肉男吗？完全没问题。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="307" data-backw="562" data-height="350" data-imgfileid="504965741" data-ratio="0.546875" data-type="gif" data-w="640" data-width="640" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPCgh796vJmWa4RiaFjXYtKEgo0F3tYv9y1WEJZqBDYpOS7ibZCca9RgtQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">后悔了，还是想让男性角色变回女性？也没问题。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="307" data-backw="562" data-height="350" data-imgfileid="504965742" data-ratio="0.546875" data-type="gif" data-w="640" data-width="640" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPTuVKpFn49Cuo7FLFqmOe0DBsbzghN1CzyBAbwlYVfNNOyricyQkXV9w/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">我们可以把这个场景中女性角色身边的男性换成一个中年黑人，或者一位衣冠楚楚的绅士。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="316" data-backw="578" data-imgfileid="504965744" data-ratio="0.546875" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="640" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPWCp50ytHnNROgHalSNmTfpyKa2qzwfUyo80kDH2H2z91jrJc2u8ibiaQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;"></span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">一个效果炸裂的电影片头怎么设计？它来帮你。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="311" data-backw="562" data-height="354" data-imgfileid="504965745" data-ratio="0.5539906103286385" data-type="gif" data-w="639" data-width="639" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPYATtj9r9Z4ERbFsEiabiahtJ1hpZY5Wic4awkafErdcLXlOf4bH6uCWoQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">公司联合创始人兼CEO Zeev Farbman表示，这款产品非常适合电影制作人、前期制作人员和广告公司等专业人士。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">「LTX Studio能够帮助快速构建概念故事，或者在不需要大量投资的情况下，帮助电影制作人评估拍摄场景的不同方案。」</span></p><h3 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 104, 39);"><strong><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">背后的模型</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;"></span></h3><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">LTX Studio结合了多种AI技术，涵盖了创作过程中的各个环节。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">其中，公司独创的文生视频模型——LongAnimateDiff，能够创作出帧数在16至64之间的视频。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">此外，团队还发布了另一款专门用于创作32帧视频的模型。与LongAnimateDiff相比，它在视频质量上通常有更出色的表现。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="111" data-backw="562" data-height="172" data-imgfileid="504965746" data-ratio="0.19770114942528735" data-type="png" data-w="870" data-width="870" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPJVJD1CWiaApKg2Od8QM4nEtNqlYt1X3cU5yZdkiaLno1KJROjM7vs32A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">不过，并不是所有的功能都依赖AI技术。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">对于背景音乐，公司选择了第三方的音乐资产供应商，因为他们认为目前的AI技术还无法创作出符合要求的背景音乐质量。</span></p><div autoid="1895" data-style-type="0" style="max-width: 100%;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div style="padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;">一大波真实制作来了！</p></div></div><h2 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"></h2><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">官方在推特上已经放出了一大波网友制作的视频，并且还分享了背后工作流的样子。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">在赛博朋克的未来城市中，一位赏金猎人的新手之旅意外地将他卷入了一场残酷的城市帮派战争。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这一切始于他在一次意外中救下了一位黑帮老大的儿子，从而引发了一系列连锁反应。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">如果他想在法律的边缘生存下去，就必须迅速适应这个充满危险和诡计的世界。</span></p><p><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3349872482983624715" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPPrcOKm5JVRvKcZc7ibT6Micbs021wKxm6hvDIicv8FfyGcQv1icE80wdGA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-w="1920" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3349872482983624715"></iframe></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">A rookie cyberpunk bounty hunter finds himself at the center of a city gang war after saving a mob bosses son from a rival attack. Gotta learn the rules fast if he wants to survive life on this side of the law. A crime thriller packed with hits, &nbsp;jealousy, and power.</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="504965748" data-ratio="0.540625" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="960" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPic7HH640Oic7f4qkzzK6GtqTmqWc3EkSOLwUS2nsuIWCk7iaaPz40IYBQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Marcus，一位身经百战的角斗士，正站在竞技场地下的昏暗房间中，进行最后的检查。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">画面中的短剑是他在无数战斗中的忠实伴侣，每一次的磨砺都是对生死的考验。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">当Marcus踏入竞技场，那刺眼的阳光和滚烫的空气仿佛预示着即将到来的战斗。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3349883370943823874" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPswIH3my7uGYfhKk11Ody4xKFdMb9uqRtLrQPEibdzDhGGVib9Cx47G1g%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-w="1024" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3349883370943823874"></iframe></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Marcus is a gladiator and in the dimly lit room beneath the arena, he prepares for battle as he checks his gladius for the last time. He steps out into the light, seeing the vast crowd in the scorching sun, he sees his opponent and softly smiles. This day belongs to him.</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="504965747" data-ratio="0.540625" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="960" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPibbPnOvCpVVcRybDmzibWW7be4N1GfNocXcK7icbLsSUBj19VCnAPNfzw/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">在这个因核灾难而变得荒凉的世界里，只有女性存活下来。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">她们佩戴的防毒面具，不仅是在这充满毒素的空气中求生的必需品，更成为了她们反抗绝望、宣示力量的象征。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">在这片满目疮痍的废墟之中，她们为争夺资源、权力以及自由，展开了殊死的斗争。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3349888444826927105" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPTufADNJBoeBCOGuggvk7ADTyJn2eY5T7jvOWfyS6BeOTZoszF1Fvsw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-w="1024" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3349888444826927105"></iframe></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">In a world scorched by nuclear disaster, where only women survive, they wear gas masks, not just for air, but as a statement. Amidst the ruins, they fight for resources, power, and freedom. In a Mad Max inspired dystopia, witness their stylish resilience.</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="504965749" data-ratio="0.540625" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="960" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPfA1K0ia6LRH4gjLC718FptMibB9ZIQXqia9NDQeowcibDt3JP3rrmrIPDA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">在一个奇妙的冒险中，一位8岁的勇敢女孩穿越时空回到了恐龙时代，却意外发现了一个充满神秘的高级文明。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">面对时间的紧迫，她不仅要想方设法修复她的时间机器，还要揭开这个古老文明的秘密，并把这些珍贵的知识带回现代。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3349899479118004225" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPPxMnsLVrCGibnV8wUahTCFp12Z7YU88pnTg6TaddNk7UDuPSYbqTEmg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-w="1920" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3349899479118004225"></iframe></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">An 8 year old girl travels back in time to see the dinosaurs and discovers an unknown advanced civilization. &nbsp;She must fix her time machine and bring back the secret on the civilization to the present before it's too late.</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="283" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504965750" data-ratio="0.5041666666666667" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="960" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPHeMN2DkbV6iaawWzQHHJaibfMbFNibxiads3Wge6HxOglGJRrr4GcwL5gw/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><div autoid="1895" data-style-type="0" style="max-width: 100%;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div style="padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;">国外网友热评十大AI电影</p></div></div><h2 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"></h2><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这些天，「AI颠覆好莱坞」的呼声，是越来越猛了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">随着Sora掀起AI视频的热潮，网友们也纷纷使用各种AI视频工具，做出了自己的电影级大片。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">国外博主Min Choi最近就评选出，全网十个效果最好的DIY电影预告片。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="430" data-backw="562" data-height="798" data-imgfileid="504965751" data-ratio="0.764367816091954" data-type="png" data-w="1044" data-width="1044" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPA1TnhmosRkWBdicsQ8fv77IW1G9BvpzcrTaDy7Y09cdZ3ibrX7ZQkib8A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><h3 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 104, 39);"><strong><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">1 怀旧宇航员</span></strong></span></h3><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这个AI短片，出自一位叫Shang Chi的网友之手。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">入选了2024年MIT AI电影制作大赛黑客马拉松的最佳影片。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Shang Chi感叹道：AI是讲故事的终极武器，如果没有伟大的AI社区灵感，自己不可能做出这个片子。</span></p><p><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3349939915614339075" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2JcebuKYC1gHHjCRAplSJPrUcfVwTUicWVahg9oGjJ7BgJXh6SovxAicjPwupLp5m7ibI2to0HPXuwg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.8305555555555555" data-w="1318" style="bo