;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;">更多「神作」来袭</p></div></div><h2 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"></h2><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这次两位作者放出的第二批视频，效果更加逼真、更加炸裂。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="480" data-backw="270" data-imgfileid="504964192" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="270" style="width: 57%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9u5aD6ibzruOlWuDyWP3SIdFC20UacfxHclYVzRFWxWOeic1WAaUe3OlA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">网友们接连不断发出惊叹：Sora是怎么做到一次比一次迭代得更好的？</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这个视频是「一名潜水员发现了一艘隐藏的未来沉船，里面有控制论海洋生物和先进的外星技术」。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="270" data-backw="480" data-imgfileid="504964193" data-ratio="0.5625" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="480" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/UicQ7HgWiaUb0RIAx2RwRGmacQ8lIe6Nr9Opy5VvVzQljtdeYxpRTZnFx5VczajhU