1024" data-imgfileid="504963382" data-ratio="1" data-type="png" data-w="1024" data-width="1024" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgblOU1PK96T1eLibXNA4PFqtmwAHbZ34FGOnDAG1jePicThhVz4rCEsPow/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">关于Stable Diffusion 3.0的核心技术进展，CEO Emd总结了一份「太长不看版」摘要——</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-height="172" data-imgfileid="504963381" data-ratio="0.14814814814814814" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1160" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbZ9QDUx8IahIwaPMbu2jXTVQ2F6T8ibiblsamqATcf2TuLjlcPeAIGjPQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"></span></p><blockquote class="js_blockquote_wrap" data-type="2" data-url="" data-author-name="" data-content-utf8-length="241" data-source-title=""><div class="js_blockquote_digest"><div><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">- 采用了与Sora类似的Diffusion Transformer技术，并结合了流匹配（Flow Matching）等多项技术改进。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">- 通过利用对Transformer的改进，不仅使得系统扩展性更强，还能处理多种类型的输入数据。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">- 将以开源形式发布，通过预览版的测试来进一步提升系统的质量和安全性。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">- 发布时，将包含一套完整的工具。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">- 基于最新硬件技术打造的新平台，可以支持多种规模的版本。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">- 支持生成视频、3D以及更多类型的内容创作。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">- 需要更多的GPU来实现更强大的计算能力。</span></p></div></div></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;"></span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">不得不说，最近这段时间，DiT实火！</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">目前，模型可选择的参数范围在800M到8B之间。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">现在，已经可以在这里加入候补名单，申请SD3的访问权限了：https://stability.ai/stablediffusion3</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><iframe class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-vidtype="2" data-mpvid="wxv_3339714114868494338" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbJU06Dr4QP0ibvbea9nFQWmricbGmfb1tA2UNK0mKaUQjzPJDjibibicBiaiaA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-w="1280" style="border-radius: 4px;" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3339714114868494338"></iframe></p><div autoid="1895" data-style-type="0" style="max-width: 100%;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div style="padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;">Stable Diffusion 3，文字渲染能力超进化</p></div></div><h2 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"></h2><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">按照prompt生成指定文字，一直以来都是文生图模型的老大难问题。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="94" data-backw="562" data-height="252" data-imgfileid="504963383" data-ratio="0.16666666666666666" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1510" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbUV9UvEibgibjP8NZSFHFjtoDk08vpDoRWI8lhm9FuXT70JbHXgySdSoA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;">从左到右：DeepFloyd IF、DALLE-2、Bing Image Creator、Midjourneyv5.2、SDXL v0.9（2023年7月）</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">但是这次，SD3模型对于prompt理解得很好，在黑板上正确写出了「go big or go home」。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">而且画面非常写实，远近位置、光影，都显得极其自然。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="768" data-imgfileid="504963384" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1344" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgb1Iw6fcvYYSNvX9QaQp7vXDsm6u3ibZ8IoQ3OfwNTjQsVlkTibiaCZgfJQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt: cinematic photo of a red apple on a table in a classroom, on the blackboard are the words "go big or go home" written in chalk.</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">提示（意译版）：这张电影级视觉效果的照片，捕捉到了一个静谧的教室瞬间，一颗鲜红的苹果静静地躺在桌子上，而在它背后的黑板上，则用醒目的粉笔字写着——「要么做大，要么回家」。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">相比之下，Midjourney的图是这样的：</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="315" data-backw="562" data-height="816" data-imgfileid="504963385" data-ratio="0.5601851851851852" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1456" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbibDpekvjc2lZE0ByXEjFcAT9KxVp5xU5Wf6LEoicdV46ShrRDyYMibTcg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Gemini Advanced / Ultra的图是这样的：</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="504963387" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbe4p9iab3wJ12biaRHfvicdBkU0nI1Owl3KOyKVIicXuO9YTGNVsQXCgIfg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">DALL-E 3的图是这样的：</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-height="1024" data-imgfileid="504963388" data-ratio="1" data-type="png" data-w="1024" data-width="1024" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbSUcsVGkIQdYvLkx0Y1fFLicYiaE0eYTeoJyAEVO4yvdSpBvnxccGVbOQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">各种形式的文字渲染，SD3 都出色地完成了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="538" data-imgfileid="504963386" data-ratio="0.5711252653927813" data-type="png" data-w="942" data-width="942" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbYAtFbOj25Cwia9OAhiblnZH1QMQT07IVE3iaZKDhO3XtIOlS8EuKqd0LA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt：Resting on the kitchen table is an embroidered cloth with the text 'good night' and an embroidered baby tiger. Next to the cloth there is a lit candle. The lighting is dim and dramatic.</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">提示：厨房桌上铺着一块精美的绣布，上面绣着「good night」字样和一只可爱的小老虎。旁边，一支蜡烛静静燃烧，散发出柔和而略带戏剧性的光影。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="686" data-imgfileid="504963389" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1200" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbM1sfjJWRx5VpMPUrGpVxy8Ke8VXiaLpm9kLSaNe99MGvcgicfbIyNvcQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt：Photo of an 90's desktop computer on a work desk, on the computer screen it says "welcome". On the wall in the background we see beautiful graffiti with the text "SD3" very large on the wall.</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">提示：一台放在工作桌上的90年代的台式电脑，屏幕上写着「welcome」。在背后的墙面上，有一幅醒目的涂鸦艺术作品，写的是「SD3」。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="686" data-imgfileid="504963390" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1200" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbr2Ww16E3typUficIh2SQbL0NAtkQU4koHibiae7cUbHJJFbrVUMNTne7A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt: Anime style illustration of a newsstand on top of a small grassy hill, on top of the newsstand we see the text "it's here!". In the background we see a big rain approaching.</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">提示：这是一幅充满动漫特色的插画，一个报刊亭坐落在一片绿意盎然的小山丘上，亭顶醒目地展示着「it's here!」的字样。而在这个宁静的场景背后，一场壮观的暴雨即将来临。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504963392" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgb6yh1PaJjriaXflZ15tGWUUbD6OzGtYMX79JWkVMKSGYDMaFordFVN5w/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt: Night photo of a sports car with the text "SD3" on the side, the car is on a race track at high speed, a huge road sign with the text "faster".</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">提示：在这幅夜幕下的摄影作品中，一辆标有「SD3」字样的运动赛车正在赛道上疾驰。背景里，一块巨大的路牌显眼地展示着「faster」一词。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="686" data-imgfileid="504963391" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1200" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgb6AQnXnibbvpUwu2S1vokojSMv5icyx4yQzst7fdic6UplPaMGERKEic0gw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt: Three transparent glass bottles on a wooden table. The one on the left has red liquid and the number 1. The one in the middle has blue liquid and the number 2. The one on the right has green liquid and the number 3.</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">提示：一张木桌上摆放着三个透明的玻璃瓶。从左至右，每个瓶子内分别充满了鲜艳的红、蓝、绿色液体。瓶子上，用数字1、2、3进行了标记。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="686" data-imgfileid="504963393" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1200" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbxXpmh5Ikgm5AgrYTcFqE5MCyVCI8GbbibdX6f43MJ4VkFOHPLTicov7A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt: Photo of a rectangular orange neon sign with the text "even more stable", the sign is on the wall in a metro station, subway speeding by in the background, perspective photo.</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Stable Diffusion 3.0能在文字渲染能力上取得显著提升，是因为Stability AI在新模型中采用了全新技术——Transformer和新增的文本编码功能。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">CEO Emad Mostaque解释说，因为上述原因，现在SD 3不仅能生成完整句子，还能保持风格的一致性。</span></p><h3 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 104, 39);"><strong><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">宇航员骑着粉色芭蕾舞裙猪，除SD 3竟然全军覆没？</span></strong></span></h3><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">处理包含多个对象的Prompt的能力，也是考核AI生图模型的一大关键指标。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">下面这个prompt，着实难倒了一大片选手——</span></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">一幅宇航员撑着粉色雨伞、骑着一只穿着芭蕾舞短裙的猪的画，猪旁边的地上是一只戴着高顶帽子的知更鸟，画面的角落里写着「stable diffusion」。</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这个prompt，要求模型正确理解对象的属性、位置，以及正确呈现字体很小的文本，着实是一道难题。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">如此要素拉满的细节要求，SD3.0全部理解，并且精确地完成了！</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">宇航员，粉色雨伞、穿着粉芭蕾舞裙的猪、戴高帽的知更鸟、角落里的字，100%符合prompt的要求。这就表明：模型很好地理解了prompt。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="768" data-imgfileid="504963394" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1344" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbFibKpBts2edxFEzERoIj3nqlNKeyTa2LPkyOM40eibhibHibOianMR9xVvg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt: a painting of an astronaut riding a pig wearing a tutu holding a pink umbrella, on the ground next to the pig is a robin bird wearing a top hat, in the corner are the words "stable diffusion"</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">对于同一prompt，其他模型的表现就落后了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">DALL-E 3画出的画倒是过关了，但它把「Diffusion」拼错了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="562" data-backw="562" data-height="1024" data-imgfileid="504963395" data-ratio="1" data-type="png" data-w="1024" data-width="1024" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbNyuiap2vptd8dwZW4NN8fm2amROC58iaKYp6OJ1eTBdURTG9ZQic1el8Q/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Bing的表现就更是离谱了，有的图中芭蕾舞裙的颜色不对，有的知更鸟站在了猪脑袋上，有的更是画面中飞满了知更鸟。而「Stable Diffusion」更是错得离谱。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="569" data-backw="562" data-height="1108" data-imgfileid="504963397" data-ratio="1.012962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1094" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbxSU6YgNFsAzROqiaqRU3ol8JoibXbtOsC9Z3yfCU7ljhbKUj8QLWaiaQg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Gemini Advanced这个差生的答案就更惨不忍睹了，除了拼写问题，画也没画对。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="512" data-backw="512" data-height="512" data-imgfileid="504963396" data-ratio="1" data-type="png" data-w="512" data-width="512" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbx84x7SUkmGZUPPaVdFibtyxXCXlibulFMA9XZXOZTEG5ibbWT7Sic2sg6A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">下面出场的，就是以画面质量精美著称的优秀文生图选手Midjourney了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">从画面美感上说，MJ依然甩其他模型一条街，但是考试就是考试，「Stable Diffusion」，它也没拼对。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="315" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504963398" data-ratio="0.5601851851851852" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbh1nb8hicIMUALicpdVE7ShARVsZxb7qajNnfFNPDoPfy3WBwIUMbkKGg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="315" data-backw="562" data-height="816" data-imgfileid="504963400" data-ratio="0.5601851851851852" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1456" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbwNrt5urShzVW8ZqDKwYibDznjy2eiakaA0kCFjRpFWENqf3ug7kophwA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">总结下来，这一道考题唯一的满分选手，就是Stable Diffusion 3！</span></p><div autoid="1895" data-style-type="0" style="max-width: 100%;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div style="padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;">和Sora同样的Diffusion Transformer架构</p></div></div><h2 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><br></h2><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">所以，Stable Diffusion 3.0为何有如此突飞猛进的表现？</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">原因在于，它采用了全新的架构设计。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Stability AI的首席执行官Emad Mostaque表示——</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">「Stable Diffusion 3 采用了Diffusion Transformer架构，这是一种新型的架构设计，与OpenAI最近推出的Sora模型采用的架构相似。」</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">在以前的Stable Diffusion版本中，并未采用Transformer技术。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">而Stable Diffusion 3.0采用了一种全新的方法，引入了Diffusion Transformer 技术。如果你对最近的爆火的sora有所了解，肯定对这个技术已经耳熟能详了。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="461" data-backw="562" data-height="856" data-imgfileid="504963399" data-ratio="0.8199233716475096" data-type="png" data-w="1044" data-width="1044" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbertGCOq0t8aKj2ztJDQgk7z2rLCWJBqVABQF3ziaysmjqIcBrsdIgfQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Transformer技术是，当前生成式AI革命的核心，广泛应用于文本生成模型中。而图像生成技术，则主要基于Diffusion模型。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Sora作者之一William和谢赛宁，在这篇论文中共同提出了Sora的基础架构。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="515" data-backw="562" data-height="990" data-imgfileid="504963403" data-ratio="0.9166666666666666" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgb52tnOlcUzOeuJUcaO7htAW9hvzVZNOtBRhV1x70FYxwGtZyZA2pvag/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;">论文地址：https://arxiv.org/abs/2212.09748</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这篇详细介绍DiTs的论文指出，这种基于扩散模型的新架构，可以用在图像patch上运行的Transformer替代了传统的U-Net架构。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">这样，DiTs方法就可以更高效地利用计算资源，并且在图像生成方面超越了其他扩散模型技术。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">一篇因「缺乏创新性」被CVPR 2023拒收的论文，竟成了Sora和Stable Diffusion 3.0的奠基之作，学术创新和工程创新的区别，着实引人深究。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="210" data-backw="562" data-height="430" data-imgfileid="504963401" data-ratio="0.3731481481481482" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1152" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbIX9bicjQNCicAJYibwtlriagFt9ZKKQ9Hnm9aSwxkW87uDEZXMbiaOXvqTA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Stable Diffusion 3.0 的另一个创新亮点，就是流匹配技术。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">一篇关于流匹配的研究论文介绍了这一新方法，它可以用于训练连续归一化流（Continuous Normalizing Flows, CNFs），以便更准确地模拟复杂的数据分布。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="98" data-backw="562" data-height="182" data-imgfileid="504963402" data-ratio="0.175" data-type="png" data-w="1040" data-width="1040" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbMiaichtI0JIOuyLWyue7nDJzI7MQ97CJv9wOA5EOiaSoN6q6caMUMtrEA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;">论文地址：https://arxiv.org/abs/2210.02747</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">研究表明，通过结合使用条件流匹配（Conditional Flow Matching, CFM）和最优传输路径，可以实现更快的训练速度、更高效的样本生成，并且在性能上超越传统的扩散路径方法。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="580" data-backw="578" data-imgfileid="504963430" data-ratio="1.003125" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="640" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbwia07rYh6rcjk94F9LCB4j0321kwwmDg2DVZFG0FQ4kE6oib9otvsLPA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">其实，Stability AI一直在探索多种新颖的图像生成技术。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">就在本月初，他们就推出了一项名为Stable Cascade的新技术。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">它基于一种名为Würstchen的先进架构，旨在提升生成图像的性能和精确度。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="305" data-backw="562" data-height="1355" data-imgfileid="504963405" data-ratio="0.5416666666666666" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" data-width="2500" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbwb1PkhaTffqEApwQ5ib9pn4xn2p1TW7DIQqOxQPKUMsL66hMibBSUFtw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><div autoid="1895" data-style-type="0" style="max-width: 100%;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div style="padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;">一大波整活来了</p></div></div><h2 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"></h2><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">在图像质量上，SD 3.0也取得了令人震惊的进步。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">「变色龙在黑色背景上的摄影棚照片特写」，它生成的图是这样的。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="768" data-imgfileid="504963406" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1344" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbVdBtqhZdXRsR1cEC2XyhCx8zfBNgqwpDhkah28ibbB0jMB9KztjJL9Q/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt：studio photograph closeup of a chameleon over a black background.</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Gemini Advanced/Ultra生图是这样的。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="562" data-backw="562" data-height="1536" data-imgfileid="504963410" data-ratio="1" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1536" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbAqPDtmBHHUQRoKRbw2BynKhaib4va9gmJbXprUtp6B4OEHRhvR45v5A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">Midjourney是这样的。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="315" data-backw="562" data-height="816" data-imgfileid="504963408" data-ratio="0.5601851851851852" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1456" style="width: 68%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgb1JKe4AHjphn51mIcOvhQogr26ZDIibJXiaUU1LlL2Mbz1cZ9xOye8vUw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">因为题干没有区分度，所以大家表现差不多。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">从更多的演示中可以看出，无论是在自然写实风景，还是在漫画、海报中，SD 3不仅做到了正确还原文字，还让文字和画面做到了很好的融合，一点都不突兀。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504963407" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgby1Zhf7cIbibKeF1rFrmiaWB7w5ibxkQ5OQoB3cvPdOVgr30QzNKGAsRag/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><blockquote data-type="quote_container" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Prompt: Trees photographed under the Milky Way, the moon and twilight shine on the Valley. The full moon appears high in the sky and the twilight glow can still be seen.</span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">再比如黑客帝国中的Neo狗。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="330" data-backw="578" data-height="768" data-imgfileid="504963445" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="1344" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbLu3WecYibYsKEDK12XTF1ibpUgICUELZjlp2t0iauicpwicRt4q5C0MfpIQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);"></span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;">威尔史密斯吃面，AI模型的终极图灵测试。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="728" data-backw="562" data-height="1122" data-imgfileid="504963446" data-ratio="1.2956120092378753" data-type="png" data-w="866" data-width="866" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbibysS27BW6jgTM8VYJmdU9ias5hlKTNGfILcAJCiaibBQVtlzr48gf4zBw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="504963409" data-ratio="0.5712962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbIsaQiazzZgEjjwborz69zqgVLWZWwPKLAeTqNduibtu1DlibJicwuAngsw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="321" data-backw="562" data-height="389" data-imgfileid="504963411" data-ratio="0.5720588235294117" data-type="png" data-w="680" data-width="680" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb1icgaHbrt8sMS051pxUnTgbTUUV5eHu7OK2mLwWnxQEUpQ6EerAibLoLJMAlibMsia3blI5TJrNdYHZQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 